headline: Is PayPal a Deep Value Stock or a Value Trap to Avoid?
summary: PayPal's stock is trading at its lowest valuation since its spin-off from eBay in 2015.  In response, PayPal is working on improving profit margins and user engagement.  PayPal Holdings (NASDAQ: PYPL) stock has taken investors on a roller-coaster ride over the past few years.
